      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just... they're so busy. i see them rushing around, trying to balance work and everything else, and then they have to come here and help me just to walk or eat. i feel like i'm just taking up space in their lives. i've always been the one taking care of everyone, and now i'm just a weight they have to carry. it doesn't feel right to keep going on like this when i'm only making things harder for them.",
